  "detailed_description": "<h1>\u8054\u7cfb\u4ea4\u6d41</h1><p>\u5982\u679c\u60a8\u65e0\u6cd5\u6b63\u5e38\u8fdb\u5165steam\u793e\u533a\u4ea4\u6d41\uff0c<br>\u6b22\u8fce\u52a0\u5165\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u4ea4\u6d41QQ\u7fa4\uff1a933067442</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/689070/extras/\u62fc\u62fc\u4e503.0-1_-_\u5ba3\u4f20\u56fe\uff08600x290\uff09.jpg?t=1545141880\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Story</strong></h2>After the unification war of the Kingdom, rebels appeared in the Capital.<br>Although the rebellion was quickly suppressed, there were still a number of remnants at large.<br>Two years later, the main character of the game, Asyula, received an order to pursue the leader of remnant rebellious forces, Awillou.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Team is composed of 2 characters with a total of 3 operational roles.<br></li><li>Exploration of field maps, interaction with NPCs and receiving tasks, transactions in stores, battles in the field when encountering enemy.<br></li><li>Turn-based combat RPG, characters can choose various operations in a battle in their turns respectively, without time limit.<br></li><li>SkillLink command: you can edit the SkillLink skills for each characters, the proper use of the SkillLink may reverse the situation.<br></li><li>Weapon proficiency: all weapons have proficiencies. Before a new weapon brings into play normally, it must be used for a period of time, or it may be no more than a skilled low-level weapon.<br></li><li>Supporter: Triggering special NPCs' events increases favorable impression to obtain their trusts and get their supports in the battle.<br></li><li>StarStone magic: you can buy or collect all kinds of [StarStone] from stores or in the fields. Equipting different StarStones will enable you use different magics.<br></li><li>The battle randomly triggers a variety of bonus. Carefully change the action orders can help you get the advantage of Bonus.<br></li><li>Environmental effects &amp; Traps in the field: there are different environmental effects and traps in the wild which are needed to deal with carefully!<br></li><li>32 achievements are available in the game.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/689070/extras/\u62fc\u62fc\u4e503.0-1_-_\u5ba3\u4f20\u56fe\uff08600x290\uff09.jpg?t=1545141880\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Story</strong></h2>After the unification war of the Kingdom, rebels appeared in the Capital.<br>Although the rebellion was quickly suppressed, there were still a number of remnants at large.<br>Two years later, the main character of the game, Asyula, received an order to pursue the leader of remnant rebellious forces, Awillou.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Team is composed of 2 characters with a total of 3 operational roles.<br></li><li>Exploration of field maps, interaction with NPCs and receiving tasks, transactions in stores, battles in the field when encountering enemy.<br></li><li>Turn-based combat RPG, characters can choose various operations in a battle in their turns respectively, without time limit.<br></li><li>SkillLink command: you can edit the SkillLink skills for each characters, the proper use of the SkillLink may reverse the situation.<br></li><li>Weapon proficiency: all weapons have proficiencies. Before a new weapon brings into play normally, it must be used for a period of time, or it may be no more than a skilled low-level weapon.<br></li><li>Supporter: Triggering special NPCs' events increases favorable impression to obtain their trusts and get their supports in the battle.<br></li><li>StarStone magic: you can buy or collect all kinds of [StarStone] from stores or in the fields. Equipting different StarStones will enable you use different magics.<br></li><li>The battle randomly triggers a variety of bonus. Carefully change the action orders can help you get the advantage of Bonus.<br></li><li>Environmental effects &amp; Traps in the field: there are different environmental effects and traps in the wild which are needed to deal with carefully!<br></li><li>32 achievements are available in the game.</li></ul>",
